title: Vinyl Season 1 Unofficial Soundtrack (HBO 2016) [320 kbps]
description:
Sex. Drugs. Rock & Roll.

This is a collection of all of the music featured in the first season of HBO's TV series "Vinyl". Everything from songs central to the plot, to the stuff playing in the background. And I think it has the most extensive tracklist of any other show ever created.

230 tracks in total, from 179 different artists. Genres vary from straight up rock & roll, punk rock and pop, to jazz, soul and folk.

If you ever wanted to hear how the 70's sounded like, now you can. Enjoy!
